class.name: MediaPipeEmbedding
class.description: A MediaPipe task data container for embedding result for a given embedder head. Only either [member float_embedding] or [member quantized_embedding] will contain data, depending on whether the embedder was configured to perform scalar quantization.

method.name: has_head_name
method.description: Returns [code]true[/code] if the embedding has [member head_name].

members.member: The head index of the embedding.
The optional head name of the embedding.
